        <h1 class="page__title title" id="page-title">Facing History Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="content">
      <div class="region region-content">
    <div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system">

    
  <div class="content">
    <div id="node-13998" class="node node-page view-mode-full clearfix">

  
      
  
  <div class="content">
    
  <div class="field-body">
    <h3>Summary of This Privacy Notice</h3>

<p>Facing History is committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy notice, together with our <a href="https://www.facinghistory.org/privacy/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>, sets out how we look after your personal data when you visit our website at <a href="https://www.facinghistory.org">www.facinghistory.org</a>, and tells you about your privacy rights and how certain laws may apply to you.</p>

<p>If you have any queries about this policy or how we use your personal information, please contact us at <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#98e8eaf1eef9fbe1d8fef9fbf1f6fff0f1ebecf7eae1b6f7eaffa7ebedfaf2fdfbeca5c8eaf1eef9fbe1bdaaa8c8f7f4f1fbe1bdaaa8d1f6e9edf1eae1"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="69191b001f080a10290f080a00070e01001a1d061b1047061b0e">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>.</p>

<p><strong>Facing History does not sell, rent, or license its customer lists to third parties. We do not sell, trade, or share any donor's personal information with any other entity, nor do we send donor mailings on behalf of other organizations. </strong></p>

<h3>Contents</h3>

<ol>
	<li><strong><a href="#about-us">About us</a></strong></li>
	<li><a href="#what-personal-data-do-we-collect-via-site"><strong>What personal data do we collect via the site?</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#how-we-collect-personal-data"><strong>How we collect personal data</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#how-why-we-use-personal-data"><strong>How and why we use personal data</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#how-we-share-personal-data"><strong>How we share personal data</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#international-transfers"><strong>International transfers</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#data-security"><strong>Data security</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#children"><strong>Children</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#how-long-we-keep-personal-data"><strong>How long we keep personal data</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#third-party-links"><strong>Third party links</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#your-rights"><strong>Your rights</strong></a></li>
	<li><a href="#changes-to-policy-your-data"><strong>Changes to this policy or your data</strong></a></li>
</ol>

<hr>
<ol>
	<li>
	<h4><a id="about-us" name="about-us">About Us</a></h4>

	<p>This website <a href="https://www.facinghistory.org">www.facinghistory.org</a> (our "<strong>site</strong>") is operated by Facing History and Ourselves, Inc. ("<strong>Facing History US</strong>") and Facing History and Ourselves Ltd ("<strong>Facing History UK</strong>"). Together, Facing History US and Facing History UK are referred to in this privacy notice as "<strong>Facing History</strong>", and also as "we", "us" and "our". Facing History US and Facing History UK are joint data controllers of any information we collect via this site.</p>

	<p>The contact details of our head offices are:</p>

	<table class="responsive">
